{"id":238458,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-北京丰台被强拆村民到中南海外散步多人/","date":"2012-07-07T20:16:10Z","modified":"2012-07-07T20:16:10Z","title":"维权网 | 北京丰台被强拆村民到中南海外散步多人遭扣押（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FRsi9R_LLTk/T_gJ-TVnrbI/AAAAAAAAJCc/OoI8stPBoz4/s1600/1.jpg\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><img border=\"0\" height=\"211\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FRsi9R_LLTk/T_gJ-TVnrbI/AAAAAAAAJCc/OoI8stPBoz4/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>宋振明等人当即被警方扣押</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>中午</span><span>，丰台区南苑乡石榴庄村村民黄玉卿、宋振明、李焕君、徐慧贞、张宗钢、姜流勇、黎建波、焦建秋、郭志英、孙双燕等人，因自己房屋于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>被村委会组织人员非法强拆，无家可归，漫无目的散步到了中南海墙外，当即被警察扣留。</span></div>\n<div><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日中午</span><span>，村民们仍然被关在派出所，被分别审问。一行人被警方羁押已超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>小时，其家属并未收到任何法律文书及司法解释。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>同样在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>房屋被强拆的村民周杰表示，我家被铁锤破门，洗劫一空警察不管，打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，派出所让我们去找村委会协商，并且说死不给受案回执，几个人胸中憋闷，去散散步，却被警察抓了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>相关信息请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_3563.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_3563.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3587993684133571002?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p